PRAIA, Cape Verde, February 13, 2018/APO Group/ -- 
                                                
                        By mid 2020, the Republic of Cabo Verde will inaugurate a continental training center dedicated to African State Security Forces. The objective of this initiative is to build capacity to face the persistent security challenges of the continent and to develop international cooperation in defense and security. The center is called « ORBIT TRAINING CENTER » (www.Orbit.training) and the cost of construction is estimated to be $125m.
        
                
            
                
                                
                
                
